			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="This PAD oneliner is said when players have gotten the curse of Mystic Carrion's ancient lair by interacting with a secret door or picking up any object in the lair. Carrion is a mummy lord, so his lair is hostile to any living creatures, Astarion won't get affected." />
